# 1Ô∏è‚É£6Ô∏è‚É£ GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

Logic 22 enforces:

* Capacity assessment mandatory for high-value awards
* Risk flags cannot be hidden
* Award justification required if selecting high-risk supplier
* Historical manipulation detection
* Cross-buyer visibility (if centralized system)

Integrated with:

* Logic 8 ‚Üí Evaluation scoring
* Logic 15 ‚Üí Performance memory
* Logic 16 ‚Üí Delivery feasibility
* Logic 21 ‚Üí Market-wide awareness

